Subject: We Appreciate Your Application and Participation

Body:
<html><body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#222222;font-size:14px;">
<p><strong>Hello [applicant_first_name],</strong></p>

<p>Thank you for taking the time to participate in the final interview for the [job_title] position. We truly appreciate the effort you invested in completing your application and sharing your experience, skills, and insights with us.</p>

<p>This message is simply to express our sincere appreciation for your time and participation in the process, regardless of the outcome.</p>

<p>We encourage you to stay connected with us and follow us on Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, and LinkedIn to stay updated on our latest hiring opportunities, which may be useful for future applications or even referrals should you join us.</p>

<p>It was a pleasure learning more about you, and we sincerely value your interest in joining Outsourced Pro Global.</p>

<p>Recruiter contact: [recruiter_phone_line]</p>

[signature]
</body></html>
